reviewText: I ordered this in hopes to enjoy this series. The second disc does not run, BUT the first one does !

Luv'd it! I also wish there were more episodes!
A funny twisted romantic cute series.
Wish there were more shows out there like this.

I have never seen a series where the main female character is actually allowed to show lust and desire for another woman. It was very funny and painfully truthful. I wish there were more than two seasons. British TV shows just seem to be so much more willing to get deep into lesbian characters than America's. So glad my player plays all regions.
